Rattrap:





Rattrap didn't like it out in the forest, but he might as well get used to 
it. It may have been his only cover.

He had to keep going and try to find something that could help him. But 
what? The only bots that he ever came in contact with were the ones that 
used him. And nothing from this planet could come to any good to him.

He kept on moving, hitting his feet against rocks and tripping over 
up-rooted little things. It took him a few more minutes until he finally 
made it out of the forest. He looked behind himself and watched the skies 
for the Predacon fliers. That was when he bumped into something (Dark 
Mouse).
